 * changelog:
 *      * Added SPDX-License-Identifier
 *      * Update to solidity ^0.8.0
 *      * Update openzeppelin imports
 *      * IRewardDistributionRecipient integrated in Unipool and removed
 *      * Added virtual and override to stake and withdraw methods
